.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, potato, grapefruit, zucchini
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, bike, taxi, snowmobile
1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the person eating zucchini is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person eating zucchini is on the far right##1
4. the person eating potato is the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is between the person eating raspberry and the person eating potato##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Food   | potato     | grapefruit           | raspberry | zucchini  |
| Transport         | skateboard | snowmobile | bike   | taxi |

