.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, video-games, writing, chess
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, january, october, march
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's hobby is writing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby   | chess   | video-games | photography | writing      |
| Birthday     | october | june    | january  | march |

