.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, april, december, june
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, mirinda, fanta
1. the person drinking milk is the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person drinking 7up is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person drinking mirinda##2
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Birthday       | september | june | december     | april   |
| Beverage   | mirinda   | 7up     | fanta | milk |

