.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, rock, house, classical
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, november, june, april
1. the fan house is between the person who's birthday is in may and the fan folk##2
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the fan folk##1
3. the fan classical is on the right of the fan folk##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the fan folk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Music-Genre         | rock | house | folk | classical |
| Birthday   | may         | april       | november    | june         |

