.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, analyst, accountant, electrician
House: tower, cape-cod, palace, gothic-revival
1. the cape-cod house is on the right of the electrician##1
2. the palace house is on the right of the accountant##1
3. the engineer is on the right of the analyst##1
4. the palace house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
5. the cape-cod house is between the analyst and the gothic-revival house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Job    | electrician   | accountant      | analyst   | engineer  |
| House   | gothic-revival | cape-cod | palace | tower |

