.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, water-polo, lacrosse, baseball
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, january, july, april
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is parkour##2
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Sport          | parkour     | water-polo | baseball   | lacrosse        |
| Birthday   | march | july   | january | april |

