.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, balloon-flower, bellflower, begonia
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, july, august, september
1. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who growsorchid##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person who growsbegonia##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Flower         | balloon-flower | bellflower | begonia | orchid |
| Birthday   | august          | july     | september  | june     |

