.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, fanta, coffee
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, pakistani, mexican, thai
1. the mexican is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking coffee is between the thai and the person drinking 7up##2
3. the pakistani is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage           | 7up | coffee | hot-chocolate | fanta     |
| Nationality   | indonesian   | mexican    | thai   | pakistani |

