.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, 7up, almond-milk
4 different games are played: go, billiard, chess, monopoly
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing go is between the person playing monopoly and the person playing billiard##2
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person playing chess is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage           | lemonade | almond-milk | 7up | hot-chocolate |
| Game   | billiard   | go | monopoly         | chess |

