The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, hip-hop, salsa, soul
1. the fan rock is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the ship is between the fan soul and the person driving the jet-ski##2
3. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
4. the fan hip-hop is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |      4       |
| Transport         | jet-ski      | ship | bus  | taxi |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | salsa  | soul | rock    |

