.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, march, may, october
City: hamburg, new-york, liverpool, nizza
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person who's birthday is in march##2
4. the person traveling to nizza is the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Birthday   | october | march | july | may |
| City           | liverpool  | nizza  | new-york | hamburg      |

