.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, almond-milk, lemonade
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, bluemaster, vegafina, alhambra
1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking coffee is between the aristoff-smoker and the person drinking almond-milk##2
4. the person drinking lemonade is the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage       | lemonade | coffee | almond-milk | iced-tea |
| Cigar   | aristoff    | bluemaster  | alhambra    | vegafina       |

