.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, quad-bike, helicopter
City: nizza, san-francisco, london, rome
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is the person traveling to nizza##1
4. the person traveling to rome is between the person driving the bus and the person driving the quad-bike##2
5. the person driving the quad-bike is the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Transport   | helicopter   | bus   | car | quad-bike |
| City         | nizza | san-francisco | rome     | london    |

