.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, scooter, van, quad-bike
House: farmhouse, cottage, wooden, futuristic
1. the cottage house is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the airplane is between the farmhouse house and the person driving the quad-bike##2
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Transport   | van    | quad-bike     | airplane | scooter |
| House     | cottage | futuristic | wooden       | farmhouse     |

 